org.jacoco.core.runtime
Class WildcardMatcher

java.lang.Object
  org.jacoco.core.runtime.WildcardMatcher

public class WildcardMatcher
extends Object

Matches strings against ?/* wildcard expressions. Multiple expressions can be separated with a colon (:). In this case the expression matches if at least one part matches.
